snippet.title: You Have To Climb Out | Announcement and Release Date trailer
snippet.description:
hi so basically i spent the last 6 months learning how to use the game engine Godot, making a few tiny/tutorial games, and then accidentally making a short puzzle game that i grew to really love.

Releasing July 15, wishlist on Steam right here please (pretty please):

https://store.steampowered.com/app/3026480/You_Have_To_Climb_Out/
